</head>

<body>
    <%- include ("../partials/aio_dld_header.ejs") %>
    
    <div class="Content">
        <p>Welcome to the AIO DLD!</p>
        <% if (user) { %>
            <p>Hello <%= user.name %>!</p>
        <% } else { %>
            <p>Please <a href="/login">Login Here</a></p>
        <% } %>
        <p>
            The All-In-One Duel Links Draft, shortened to AIO DLD, is an all-in-one application<br>
            that allows users to pull cards from Duel Links boxes, organize those cards into decks,<br>
            trade cards with other users, and view all the cards available all in one place!<br>
            It's built especially for players and practitioners of the Duel Links Draft format!<br>
        </p>
